## Output Files

### PLINK 2 format (default)

| File | Description |
|------|-------------|
| `{prefix}.pgen` | Binary genotype matrix |
| `{prefix}.pvar` | Tab-delimited variant metadata |
| `{prefix}.psam` | Tab-delimited sample metadata |

### PLINK 1 format (`VERSION 1`)

| File | Description |
|------|-------------|
| `{prefix}.bed` | Binary genotype matrix (PLINK 1 encoding) |
| `{prefix}.bim` | Tab-delimited variant metadata (6 columns) |
| `{prefix}.fam` | Tab-delimited sample metadata (6 columns) |

