## Risk Assessment

| Risk | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|--------|------------|
| COPY TO API complexity | Implementation difficulty | Fall back to table function |
| pgenlib_write.cc build issues | Can't produce compressed .pgen | Phase 1 uses uncompressed |
| Schema validation for arbitrary queries | Wrong columns silently produce bad files | Strict column name/type checking |
| File atomicity (partial writes) | Corrupt output | Write to temp files, rename on success |

